column2: Ryouma! The Prince of Tennis Shinsei Movie: Tennis no Ouji-sama

The film will feature an original story that takes place during the three months following the ending of Tennis no Ouji-sama and the beginning of its sequel Shin Tennis no Ouji-sama.

(Source: MAL News)
